<section class="c-landing-section c-landing-section--bordered">
  <div class="c-explanation-showcase--centered c-explanation-showcase--wider">
    <h2 class="text-center c-explanation-showcase__heading">About us</h2>
    <p class="text-center c-explanation-showcase__copy">
      Honeypot is a developer-focused job platform, on a mission to get every developer a great job.
      We believe developers should have all the information they need to choose a job they love: whether that’s based on a cutting-edge tech stack, an inspiring team or just good old-fashioned salary.
      In our world, that means no more spam and empty promises from headhunters, no more sending the same application to multiple companies - just one profile and the choice to receive  honest offers related to your job preferences direct from companies.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="c-landing-section">
  <div class="c-explanation-showcase--centered">
    <h2 class="text-center c-explanation-showcase__heading">Meet the team</h2>
