      "But this isn’t just some Craigslist directory – far from it. Honeypot offers a Talent Rep to each person looking for work.
      They’re like a guide to help you  land the best job to suit your current aspirations.
      It’s a very straightforward system meant to target the best mid-to-advanced developers currently seeking employment.”
    </p>
    <p class="push--top--double">
